Home > Music > Alessia Cara Nails Impressions Of Nicki Minaj, Ariana Grande & Lorde On Fallon Alessia Cara Nails Impressions Of Nicki Minaj, Ariana Grande & Lorde On Fallon 1 1 Posted by Zakk Feig , Feb 4, 2017 at 07:19pm Alessia Cara is a beast with impressions. 
Alessia Cara may have been the best impressionist Fallon's had on his show thus far. The Canadian singer absolutely killed her impressions of Ariana Grande , Nicki Minaj and Lorde during the "Wheel of Musical Impressions" segment on "The Tonight Show," and Fallon lost his mind witnessing it. 
Fallon is a solid impressionist, doing his best to imitate Axl Rose and Sting. Despite his best efforts, Fallon could not stand up to Alessia Cara's prowess.
